                     </author>
                        <editor role="scr" key="person_f859"><persName role="scr" xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc" key="person_f859">Ciġālazādah Darvīsh Maḥmūd ibn al-Ḥājj ‘Abd al-Karīm</persName><lb/>
